          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "于龙凤阁严词谏阻，李妃执迷不听，君臣争辩甚剧，不欢而散。李良封锁了昭阳院，使内外隔绝，篡位之"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "迹已明。徐、杨二人于探皇灵后，二次进宫进谏。此时李妃已悔悟，遂以国事相拖。后杨波发动人马，卒斩"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李良。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "注释"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "《二进宫》是全部《龙凤阁》剧中的一折，唱腔有特殊成就。此本现由杨宝森与中国京剧团演员雪艳琴、王"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "泉奎和本院（中国戏曲研究院）编辑处祁野耘，共同作了一些词句上的修润。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "根据《京剧丛刊》第十七集整理"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉！先王啊……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（宫女、徐小姐、李艳妃同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "自那日与徐杨决裂以后，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "看一看不觉是八月中秋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "太师爷起下了篡位奸谋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "竟把我孤儿寡母当作了马牛。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "怕的是太师爷来把宫搜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "先王爷晏了驾太子年幼"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "他那里父女情全然无有"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "徐小姐把守在宫门口"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大人请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千岁请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐延昭、杨波、杨公子同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "探罢皇灵到昭阳，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "宫门上锁是贼李良。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "铜锤付与大人掌，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨波接锤，交付杨公子。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "击开宫门见皇娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨公子",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "铜锤一举双环断，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐小姐",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "何人大胆闯昭阳？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭、杨波",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿休要动手，此乃（杨四公子）（徐小姐），向前见礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨公子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小将有礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "还礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨公子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我儿启奏国太：就说徐、杨二家宫门候旨求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐小姐进内。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启奏国太：徐、杨二家宫门候旨求见。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宣他二人进宫！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐小姐",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "国太有旨：徐杨二家进宫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此番进宫，将保国之事，启奏国太。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "全仗千岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大人请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千岁请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "千岁爷进寒宫休要慌忙，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "站宫门听学生细说比方："
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "鸿门设宴要害汉王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "九里山前摆下战场。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "到后来封韩信三齐王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "后宫院有一位吕后娘娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "三宣韩信命丧未央。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "盖世忠良不能久长。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "千岁爷进寒宫学生不往。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "昔日里楚汉两争强"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "张子房背宝剑把韩信来访"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "逼得个楚项羽乌江命丧"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "他朝中有一位萧何丞相"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "君臣们摆下了天罗地网"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "九月十三雪霜降"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怕者何来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "怕的是辜负了十年寒窗、九载遨游、八月科场、七篇文章，才落得个兵部侍郎，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "怕只怕无有下场！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "说什么学韩信命丧未央，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "站宫门听老夫改说一桩："
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "龙国太怎比得吕后皇娘；"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "大人怎比三齐王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "有老夫比樊哙、怀抱铜锤、保驾身旁，料也无妨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "先王爷怎比得汉高皇上"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "李良贼怎比得萧何丞相"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "这寒宫权当作鸿门宴上"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我好比鱼儿闯过了千层罗网，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "受了些惊怕，着了些慌忙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "只要你忠心把国掌，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "老夫保你满门无伤"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "千岁爷保学生满门无伤，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "舍死忘生闯进昭阳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "前面走的开国将，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "后面跟随兵部侍郎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "站立在宫门朝内望，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先王啊……"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "又只见龙国太怀抱太子、两泪汪汪、口口声声哭的是先王！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "龙国太哭的是江山难掌，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "摆一摆手儿切莫要承当。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "进宫去休行那君臣大礼，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "学一个文站东，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "武列西，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨波 （同二黄原板） 各自分班站立在两厢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先王啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "李艳妃坐昭阳前思后想，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "想起了朝中事无有主张。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "想必是徐、杨进了昭阳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我只得怀抱太子、两泪汪汪、口口声声哭的是先王！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "耳边厢又听得朝靴底响"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄慢板",
          "musical_style": "二黄慢板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "有几句话儿我不好言讲"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "怀抱着幼主爷江山执掌，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "为什么恨天怨地，假带愁肠所为那桩？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "并非是哀家假带愁肠，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "都只为我朝中不得安康。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我朝中有什么祸从天降？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你就该请太师进宫来，父女们商量又待何妨？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "太师爷心肠如同王莽，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "他要夺我皇儿锦绣家邦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "太师爷娘娘的父，他本是皇亲国丈，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "未必他一旦无情，起下了篡位的心肠。太师爷忠良！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你道他无有那篡位的心肠，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "封锁昭阳为的是哪桩？"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "臣七月十三也曾把三本奏上，国太偏偏要让，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你言道：大明朝有事无事、不用徐杨二奸党，赶出朝房，龙国太自立为王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "先前的话儿休要讲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不看哀家看在先王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我封你一字并肩王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "徐王兄保幼主登龙位上"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "老臣年迈难把国掌，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "要保国还是那兵部侍郎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "徐王兄年纪迈难把国掌，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "转面来叫一声兵部侍郎："
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你的名儿万古扬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你保幼主登龙位上"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "吓得臣低头不敢望，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "战战兢兢启奏皇娘："
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "今日里进宫来辞别皇娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "放臣还乡落得个安康。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "臣昨晚修下了辞王本"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "望国太开恩将臣放"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "他二人把话一样讲，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "倒叫哀家无有主张。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "无奈何怀抱太子跪在昭阳"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "吓坏了定国王！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "兵部侍郎！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "自从盘古立帝邦，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "君跪臣来臣怎敢当！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "非是哀家来跪你，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "跪的是我皇儿锦绣家邦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "锦家邦来锦家邦，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "臣有一本启奏皇娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "昔日里有一个李文、李广，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "弟兄双双扶保朝纲；"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "李文北门带箭丧，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "伴驾山前又收李刚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "收了一将损伤一将，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "一将倒比一将强。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "到后来保太子登龙位上，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "反把那李广斩首在法场。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "这都是前朝的忠臣良将，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "哪一个忠良又有下场？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "有下场来无下场，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "细听哀家说个比方："
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "李氏夫人替了皇娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "他的名儿万古扬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "昔日里有个潘老丞相"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "紫竹林内生太子"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "困龙思想长江浪，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "虎落平阳想奔山岗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "国太思来国太想，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "谁是忠良哪个是奸党？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "忠良本是徐、杨将，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "奸党本是我父李良。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "哀家跪死在昭阳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "二卿不把国来掌"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "铜锤一举娘娘请上，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "杨波搀起定国王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "回头来奏一道太平表章，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "老杨波搬来了众家儿郎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "听说是杨波搬兵到，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不由哀家喜眉梢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李艳妃",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "太子交与小姐抱"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐小姐",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "双手付与老年高。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "用手接过大明后，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大人！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你保幼主坐龙楼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "用手接过龙一条，"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "两眼睁睁把臣瞧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "低下头来生计巧……"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千岁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "浑身上下似水浇，难以保朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "大人不必生计巧，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "莫不是保幼主嫌官小……"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是与不是？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你的心事某猜着"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨波",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨波 （同笑） 哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐延昭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
